<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Optional_Supplementary_Text_Readings">Optional Supplementary Text Readings</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Jerry A. Coyne: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Why-Evolution-True-Jerry-Coyne/dp/B002ZNJWJU">Why Evolution Is True</a></li>
<li>Anthony J.F. Griffiths: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Introduction-Genetic-Analysis-Anthony-Griffiths/dp/1429229438/">Introduction to Genetic Analysis</a></li>
<li>Scott Freeman: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Evolutionary-Analysis-Scott-Freeman/dp/0132275848/">Evolutionary Analysis</a></li>
</ul>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Popular_books_on_Evolution">Popular books on Evolution</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Ernst Mayr: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/What-Evolution-Is-Ernst-Mayr/dp/0465044255/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I3BTH0VQEK8JE0">What Evolution Is</a></li>
<li>Carl Zimmer: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/At-Waters-Edge-Fingers-Whales/dp/0684856239/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pdT1_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I1C939R6SLD00K">At the Water's Edge&#160;: Fish with Fingers, Whales with Legs, and How Life Came Ashore but Then Went Back to Sea</a></li>
<li>Carl Zimmer: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Evolution-Triumph-Idea-Carl-Zimmer/dp/0060958502/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I3OQ4UG7CZZ70E">Evolution: The Triumph of an Idea</a></li>
<li>Sean B. Carroll: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Endless-Forms-Most-Beautiful-Science/dp/0393060160/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I3H4Z8D5WOKW6W">Endless Forms Most Beautiful: The New Science of Evo Devo and the Making of the Animal Kingdom</a></li>
<li>Richard Dawkins: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/The-Ancestors-Tale-Pilgrimage-Evolution/dp/061861916X/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pdT1_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I3K3EYDZRGIE95">The Ancestor's Tale: A Pilgrimage to the Dawn of Evolution</a></li>
<li>Richard Dawkins: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/The-Selfish-Gene-Edition-Introduction/dp/0199291152/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pdT1_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I1EDG6HDI9KOAX">The Selfish Gene</a></li>
<li>Richard Dawkins: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Greatest-Show-Earth-Evidence-Evolution/dp/1416594795/">The Greatest Show on Earth: The Evidence for Evolution</a></li>
<li>Richard Fortey: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Life-Natural-History-First-Billion/dp/037570261X/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I3MDD8OE7U91UN">Life: A Natural History of the First Four Billion Years of Life on Earth</a></li>
<li>Richard Fortey: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Trilobite-Eyewitness-Evolution-Richard-Fortey/dp/0375406255/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I2EI5DU2H6Q4QP">Trilobite!: Eyewitness to Evolution</a></li>
<li>Steve Jones: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Darwins-Ghost-Origin-Species-Updated/dp/0345422775/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=IC4SX8U662AEP">Darwin's Ghost: The Origin of Species Updated</a></li>
<li>Jared M. Diamond: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/s/ref=ntt_athr_dp_sr_1?_encoding=UTF8&amp;field-author=Jared%20M.%20Diamond&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;search-alias=books&amp;sort=relevancerank">The Third Chimpanzee: The Evolution and Future of the Human Animal</a></li>
<li>Carl Sagan: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Dragons-Eden-Speculations-Evolution-Intelligence/dp/0345346297/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1350341855&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=dragons+of+eden">The Dragons of Eden: Speculations on the Evolution of Human Intelligence</a></li>
<li>Daniel Dennet: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/DARWINS-DANGEROUS-IDEA-EVOLUTION-MEANINGS/dp/068482471X/ref=sr_1_5?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1350341935&amp;sr=1-5&amp;keywords=the+most+dangerous+idea">Darwin's Dangerous Idea: Evolution and the Meanings of Life</a></li>
<li>Stephen Jay Gould: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Bully-Brontosaurus-Reflections-Natural-History/dp/039330857X/ref=sr_1_1?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1350342315&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=bully+for+brontosaurus">Bully for Brontosaurus: Reflections in Natural History</a></li>
<li>Matt Ridley: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Genome-Autobiography-Species-Chapters-P-S/dp/0060894083/">Genome: The Autobiography of a Species in 23 Chapters</a></li>
<li>Jonathan Weiner: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Beak-Finch-Story-Evolution-Time/dp/067973337X">The Beak of the Finch: A Story of Evolution in Our Time</a></li>
<li>Olivia Judson: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Dr-Tatianas-Sex-Advice-Creation/dp/0805063323">Dr. Tatiana's Sex Advice to All Creation: The Definitive Guide to the Evolutionary Biology of Sex</a></li>
</ul>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Classics">Classics</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Charles Darwin: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Origin-Species-Barnes-Classics-Series/dp/1593080778/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=NNPYAT3YIEQ9&amp;coliid=I12W40L7X8FKA5">On the Origin of Species</a></li>
<li>Charles Darwin: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/The-Descent-Man-Penguin-Classics/dp/0140436316/ref=pd_cp_b_0">The Descent of Man</a></li>
</ul>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Evolution_vs._Creationism">Evolution vs. Creationism</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Eugenie C. Scott: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Evolution-vs-Creationism-An-Introduction/dp/0520246500/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&amp;coliid=I3USS0AICYVFKG">Evolution vs. Creationism: An Introduction</a></li>
<li>Taner Edis: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Why-Intelligent-Design-Fails-Creationism/dp/081353433X/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_nS_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&amp;coliid=I2DW7CU85E33E5">Why Intelligent Design Fails: A Scientific Critique of the New Creationism</a></li>
<li>Mark Perakh: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Unintelligent-Design-Mark-Perakh/dp/1591020840/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&amp;coliid=IRWY6OYERAYZA">Unintelligent Design</a></li>
<li>Barbara Forrest: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Creationisms-Trojan-Horse-Intelligent-Design/dp/0195157427/ref=wl_it_dp_o_pC_S_nC?ie=UTF8&amp;colid=1GXBAAITMAONF&amp;coliid=IZ4QIB19YNYCQ">Creationism's Trojan Horse: The Wedge of Intelligent Design</a></li>
</ul>
<h2> <span class="mw-headline" id="Books_for_Children">Books for Children</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Richard Dawkins: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Magic-Reality-Know-Whats-Really/dp/1451675046/">The Magic of Reality: How We Know What's Really True</a></li>
<li>Daniel Loxton: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Evolution-How-Living-Things-Came/dp/1554534305/">Evolution: How We and All Living Things Came to Be</a></li>
<li>Lisa Westberg Peters: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.amazon.com/Our-Family-Tree-Evolution-Story/dp/0152017720/">Our Family Tree: An Evolution Story</a></li>
</ul>
